# Student Management System API Tests
# Use with REST Client extension in VS Code or similar tools

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:5000/

### Get All Students
GET http://localhost:5000/api/students

### Create Student
POST http://localhost:5000/api/students
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Alice Johnson",
  "email": "alice@example.com",
  "course": "Engineering",
  "age": 21
}

### Create Another Student
POST http://localhost:5000/api/students
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Bob Wilson",
  "email": "bob@example.com",
  "course": "Business Administration",
  "age": 24
}

### Get Single Student (Replace :id with actual student ID)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/students/REPLACE_WITH_ACTUAL_ID

### Update Student (Replace :id with actual student ID)
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/students/REPLACE_WITH_ACTUAL_ID
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Alice Smith",
  "age": 22
}

### Delete Student (Replace :id with actual student ID)
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/students/REPLACE_WITH_ACTUAL_ID

### Test Validation Errors
POST http://localhost:5000/api/students
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "A",
  "email": "invalid-email",
  "course": "Invalid Course",
  "age": 15
}

### Test Duplicate Email
POST http://localhost:5000/api/students
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Another Alice",
  "email": "alice@example.com",
  "course": "Medicine",
  "age": 25
}